Highlights
==========

We got in touch with the journalists that reported how feminists in Mexico were spied by the army: <https://nocallaronlasolas.serendipia.digital/>.

We improved Persistent Storage behavior and UX in corner-cases ([[!tails_mr 1010]]).

We have started tests of the new Persistent Storage. As you might remember, there was a big revamp in [[Tails 5.8|news/version_5.8]]. The new implementation has been designed to have a smoother UI.

Releases
========

[[Tails 5.11 was released on March 20|news/version_5.11]]:

it improves performance on low-memory systems, and improves your ability to record screencasts.

Metrics
=======

Tails has been started more than 740000 times this month. This makes 23884 boots a day on average.
